Stay Safe Online Checklist:

- Never share your OTP, PIN, or passwords with anyone
- Do not approve unknown UPI payment requests
- Always verify the sender before making any payment
- Use only official and trusted payment apps
- Enable SMS and app notifications for transactions
- Avoid using public Wi-Fi for financial transactions
- Check UPI ID and details carefully before sending money
- Keep your apps and devices updated regularly
- Report suspicious activity immediately on cybercrime.gov.in
- Call helpline 1930 in case of financial fraud
